*priority is set to 0/1/2 which corresponds to LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH
*status is no longer required, and will be set to default false (uncompleted)

	* d/ - deadline
	* pr/ - priority
	* proj/ - project

commitResults.messageBody:
With the command: issue -m ISSUE_ID,
Issue with the specified issue_id is marked as complete if it is currently incomplete and marked as incomplete if it is currently complete

* changed mark command to mark issue identified with issue_id as complete
* unmark command marks issue identified with issue_id as incomplete
